(42, 9, 24, 44, 20, 23, 24, 'lose his life for my sake', 'Life and Sacrifice Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of valuing one''s life in relation to service and sacrifice. Luke highlights losing one''s life for Jesus'' sake, while Acts reflects Paul''s willingness to not count his life dear to himself for the sake of his ministry.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 9, 24, 66, 2, 10, 10, 'lose his life for my sake', 'Life and Faithfulness Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of sacrificing one''s life for a greater purpose. Luke highlights losing life for Christ''s sake, while Revelation encourages faithfulness unto death for the crown of life.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini')
